BALANCE

balance is the central citizen of exchange_ledger
it holds the running net of warmth_credit minus harm_debt across any given relationship
balance is what is reported when other parts of the body ask "how is this relationship going right now"
balance is dynamic: it shifts moment by moment as new interactions credit or debit it

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe exchange_ledger.zc
observe warmth_credit.rana
observe harm_debt.rana
observe negative_streak.rana
observe ledger.rana

the 7 properties of balance:
1 ENERGY half: holds an active value, never empty
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE neutral at the start of a relationship, drifts positive or negative with experience
5 COHERENCE nine tenths
6 COUPLING half with all the other ledger citizens
7 OBSERVER half

VERB integrate
sum the warmth_credit and harm_debt currents flowing into balance
the result is the present net

VERB report
when the immune system or any other body region asks the current state of a relationship, return balance's value

a balance is not a credit score
a credit score reflects financial trustworthiness; balance reflects emotional and behavioral trustworthiness in a specific relationship
each relationship has its own balance; fadriel's balance with his father is separate from his balance with anyone else he ever interacts with
